      "span_text": "To search for genes involved in the remarkable tolerance to acetic acid in a Z. bailii-related strain we looked for suppressors of the susceptibility phenotype of S. cerevisiae BY4741_haa1Δ through the transformation of this strain with a previously constructed genomic library from the highly tolerant Z. bailii-derived interspecies hybrid strain ISA1307  .",
